data.description: Motivated seller!  Willing to negotiate buyer closing costs.  This home is FHA assumable with a 3.375% interest rate! Seller willing to repaint interior wall color of buyer's choice with reasonable offer. Located in The Village, this home features a spacious living room and nice dining space located off of the kitchen, and 3 large bedrooms with lots of storage space. The converted garage has bonus space which could be used as an office, game room, second living or play room.   Updated floors, windows, stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops in kitchen, designer lighting, new fans, new roof 2020, and attic insulated in 2020.  Huge corner lot, with newer fence, and storage shed. Close to May Ave for easy access to restaurants and shopping. Nest thermostat, washer and dryer to stay with the home. Refrigerator negotiable.   Playset and ring camera reserved.
